<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Medox - Front Page</title>
    <style>
      /* General Body Styling */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #2c3e50; /* Dark gray-blue color */
        color: #ecf0f1; /* Light text color */
      }

      /* Navbar Styling */
      nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        background-color: #34495e;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      nav .logo {
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #ecf0f1;
      }

      nav ul {
        list-style: none;
        display: flex;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      nav ul li {
        margin: 0 10px;
      }

      nav ul li a {
        color: #ecf0f1;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 18px;
        padding: 5px 10px;
        border-radius: 5px;
        transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
      }

      nav ul li a:hover {
        background-color: #1abc9c;
      }

      /* Main Section */
      main {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 50px 20px;
      }

      main .highlight {
        color: #1abc9c;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      /* Footer Section */
      footer {
        background-color: #34495e;
        padding: 20px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      footer h2 {
        margin-bottom: 10px;
        color: #1abc9c;
      }

      footer p {
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      /* Footer Images - Boxes */
      .footer-images {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-around;
        flex-wrap: wrap; /* Ensures responsiveness */
        gap: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
      }

      .box {
        background-color: #2c3e50;
        border-radius: 10px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        overflow: hidden;
        transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
        width: 300px;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .box:hover {
        transform: translateY(-10px);
        box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
      }

      .box img {
        width: 100%;
        height: 200px;
        object-fit: cover; /* Ensures uniform image size */
      }

      .box h3 {
        margin: 15px 0;
        color: #1abc9c;
      }

      .box p {
        margin: 0 10px 15px;
        color: #bdc3c7;
      }
      .medox-info {
        background-color: #34495e; /* Dark background */
        color: #ecf0f1; /* Light text color */
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px; /* Rounded corners */
        box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
        margin: 40px auto;
        max-width: 800px; /* Restrict width for better presentation */
        text-align: center;
      }

      .medox-info p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- Navbar -->
    <nav>
      <div class="logo">Medox</div>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="/login">Log In</a></li>
        <li><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>

    <!-- Body Section -->
    <main>
      <h1>Welcome to <span class="highlight">Medox</span>!</h1>
      <p>Your companion in managing medications effectively.</p>
    </main>

    <!-- Footer -->
    <footer>
      <p>
        Our system simplifies medicine management for older people and their
        families.
      </p>
      <div class="footer-images">
        <div class="box">
          <img src="images/Granny.jpeg" alt="Granny Taking Pills" />
          <h3>Care for Yourself</h3>
          <p>Manage your medications independently with ease using Medox.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
          <img src="images/granpa.jpeg" alt="Daughter Giving Medicine" />
          <h3>Lighten the Load</h3>
          <p>Effortlessly manage care schedules for your loved ones.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="box">
          <img src="images/pills.jpeg" alt="Pills" />
          <h3>Track Every Dose</h3>
          <p>Stay on top of your medications with smart tracking features.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h2>About Medox</h2>

      <section class="medox-info">
        <p>
          Medox is a smart and user-friendly solution designed to make
          medication management effortless and stress-free. Medox ensures that
          older individuals can manage their medications independently,
          promoting their confidence and well-being. For caregivers, it reduces
          the mental burden of keeping track of multiple prescriptions, offering
          a centralized platform that simplifies schedules and avoids errors.
          Medox is not just a toolâ€”it's a companion that brings peace of mind,
          health, and harmony to families.
        </p>
      </section>

      <p>&copy; Medicine management system by Dixita 2024</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
